snippet.title: ZaraMichaela -
snippet.description:
Firstly a huge warm hello from me to you and welcome to my channel!

Im Zara, a 27 year old average lady from south wales, in the UK! 
I am a mum of two beautiful children, Blake(16 months) & Avayah(5 months)
 crazily making them eleven months apart! (i know, im very brave).

I decided to start my channel in order of a way to record and capture my life and memories of my children growing up, its such a wonderful and beautiful experience and i have decided to share it with you.

What you can expect to see from my channel is, real life honest day to day parenting with two under two, as well as chatty videos, hauls, home deco, beauty, tutorials, advice, tips & everything in-between.  

So if you think my channel is something of interest to yourselves,  grab a cuppa tea and come join us on this journey, after all its free! :)

Much Love
Zara
x
